              <zone forceUpdate='true' h='38972' id='15' type-v2='text' w='13733' x='85850' y='60266'>
                <formatted-text>
                  <run bold='true' fontcolor='#555555' fontname='Tableau Semibold' fontsize='11' underline='true'>Key Takeaways</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='10'>Shorts drove the most reach, making them the strongest format for broad audience exposure.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='10'>Interview/Press generated the highest discussion rate and strongest sentiment, but lower engagement efficiency.</run>
                  <run>Æ&#10;&#10;</run>
                  <run fontname='Tableau Medium' fontsize='10'>General Team Content and Playoff Stakes accounted for most views, showing that both routine team storytelling and postseason moments drove audience attention.</run>
                </formatted-text>
                <zone-style>
                  <format attr='border-color' value='#000000' />
                  <format attr='border-style' value='none' />
                  <format attr='border-width' value='0' />
